title: Extra 2.12.2 - WordPress Theme by ElegantThemes
description: Visit us on: https://www.nulledforums.org Extra WordPress Theme takes the Divi Builder framework and extends its advanced Drag & Drop builder power to work on your homepage and categories with a brand new set of post-based modules. Extra WordPress Theme comes with a new set of Divi Builder Plugin modules built specifically for the needs of bloggers and online publications. These new modules can be used to build a variety of different homepage and category layouts. Now you can built a post feed to meets the needs of your unique content. Extra WordPress Template is more than a theme. No longer are you limited to a single static design, or a set of pre-made layouts. Using the Divi Builder, you have complete control over the content and the structure of the category layouts you build. You don’t need to be an advanced developer to create amazing things with Extra WordPress The Divi Builder does the hard work for you, turning your ideas into a fully functional and modern design. Simply pick and choose from the Divi Builder’s wide range of content modules and arrange them on the page using its intuitive drag & drop interface. In addition to standard blog posts, Extra also expands on two other important areas: Projects and Products. If you are a designer looking to showcase your recent work, Extra makes it dead simple. Looking to sell products to your readers? Extra WordPress Theme makes that easy too with perfect WooCommerce integration. Extra WordPress Theme Features Category Builder Post & Page Builder Fully Responsive Ratings & Reviews eCommerce Ready Elegant Design
